comments: Edwards (BKN) makes marginal contact with Boucher (TOR) as both players extend for the rebound.
Duke Jr. (BKN) moves alongside VanVleet's (TOR) path to the basket and reaches in and makes contact to the ball.
Barnes (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position while contesting the play at the basket by Duke Jr. (BKN)

Replay review of the foul called on Barnes (TOR) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful and the call was overturned, as Barnes cleanly dislodges the ball from Durant (BKN) during his drive to the basket.
Griffin (BKN) places a hand on Siakam's (TOR) upper body and uses that to push himself up the contact affects Siakam's ability to pursue the rebound.
Barnes (TOR) deflects the pass from Durant (BKN) and is last to make contact with the ball before it goes OOB.
Durant (BKN) places his hand momentarily to Barnes' (TOR) shoulder and disengages off ball prior to the hand off.
Duke (BKN) makes marginal contact to VanVleet's (TOR) side prior to him beginning his upward shooting motion.
Siakam (TOR) is firming up on his right foot and makes marginal contact to Mills' (BKN) side during the screen.
Siakam (TOR) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Barnes (TOR) dislodges Durant (BKN) from his position during the rebound.

Replay review of the foul called on Griffin (BKN) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful. As Griffin (BKN) places a hand/arm to the front of VanVleet (TOR) on the drive and the contact affects his SQBR.
Boucher (TOR) makes contact to Duke Jr.'s (BKN) arm as he gains control of rebound.
Barnes (TOR) makes contact to Duke Jr.'s (BKN) body on the drive that affects his SQBR.
Siakam (TOR) commits a take foul on Mills (BKN).
